Budem sa snažiť.

56
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:39,320
Do rána si pracovala,

57
00:06:39,490 --> 00:06:41,290
nemala by si dnes ísť do školy.

58
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,990
Lenže ja chcem zmaturovať.

59
00:06:53,210 --> 00:06:56,010
Aspoň strednú by som mala dokončiť.

60
00:07:34,650 --> 00:07:37,620
Sukňa sa ti hodí.

61
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:46,450
Ty budeš Beat, však?
Ja som Minami, interiérová dizajnérka.

62
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:50,090
Dobrý deň.

63
00:07:57,610 --> 00:07:58,630
Vďaka.

64
00:08:02,980 --> 00:08:05,950
Šéf, prišiel Beat.

65
00:08:20,700 --> 00:08:22,460
To nie je na hranie, ruky preč.

66
00:08:27,970 --> 00:08:28,960
Je to vulgárne.

67
00:08:29,470 --> 00:08:31,300
To jej tam dal kto?

68
00:08:32,170 --> 00:08:36,010
Máte vôbec farebný cit?

69
